@both:<br />
Make sure you're using the latest <a href="https://triangle.codeplex.com/SourceControl/latest" rel="nofollow">source code</a>. And using the ConformingDelaunay option is always a good idea when working with Voronoi diagrams.<br />
<br />
@Gonzorob:<br />
You are adding incorrect segment indices to the geometry.<br />

@wo80: Thanks for the help. <br />
<br />
As for my case setting the quality behaviour of the mesh solved my problem.<br />
